{"tha-ap38:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap38:0.2":"Kundadhanavagga ","tha-ap38:0.3":"6 Adhimuttattheraapadana ","tha-ap38:1.1":"“Nibbute lokanathamhi, ","tha-ap38:1.2":"atthadassinaruttame; ","tha-ap38:1.3":"Upatthahim bhikkhusangham, ","tha-ap38:1.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap38:2.1":"Nimantetva bhikkhusangham, ","tha-ap38:2.2":"Ujubhutam samahitam; ","tha-ap38:2.3":"Ucchuna mandapam katva, ","tha-ap38:2.4":"Bhojesim sanghamuttamam. ","tha-ap38:3.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap38:3.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap38:3.3":"Sabbe satte abhibhomi, ","tha-ap38:3.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap38:4.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap38:4.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap38:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap38:4.4":"ucchudanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap38:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap38:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap38:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap38:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma adhimutto thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap38:7.1":"Adhimuttattherassapadanam chattham. "}